1) cd fluffos-2*
2) ./configure dw
3) make
4) make install
5) cd ../lib/secure
6) vi master.c

change "cratylus" to whatever your admin's name will be

7) cd ../../bin
8) vi dw.cfg

change the following entries:

name
mudlib directory
binary directory
external_port_1

9) ./driver ./dw.cfg &
10) telnet localhost 1701

or whatever the port number is you specified

Enjoy!

If you run into trouble, feel free to post on the Discworld
section of http://lpmuds.net/forum


